trans-unit.source: Represents a class that manages the current instance of a <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowActivity"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en klasse som administrerer den gjeldende forekomsten av en <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowActivity"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] This class also provides the query interface over the current instance of the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowActivity>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]Denne klassen gir deg også spørringsgrensesnittet over den gjeldende forekomsten av <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowActivity>.</xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowActivity>

trans-unit.source: By using an instance of this class, you can make various queries on the StateMachineWorkflowInstance.
trans-unit.target: Du kan gjøre forskjellige spørringer i StateMachineWorkflowInstance ved hjelp av en forekomst av denne klassen.

trans-unit.source: Typical queries that can be made are as follows: - Current state of the state machine.
trans-unit.target: Vanlige spørringer som kan gjøres er som følger: – gjeldende tilstand for maskin for tilstand.

trans-unit.source: - Possible transitions from the current state.
trans-unit.target: -Mulig overføringer fra den gjeldende tilstanden.

trans-unit.source: - History of transitions for the state machine instance.
trans-unit.target: -Historikk over overføringer for tilstand maskinen forekomsten.

trans-unit.source: - Enumeration of all the states in the state machine.
trans-unit.target: -Nummerering for alle tilstander i maskin for tilstand.

trans-unit.source: This property only returns the state history if the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService> is used.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen bare returnerer tilstand loggen hvis den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService>brukes.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService>

trans-unit.source: An `InvalidOperationException` occurs if the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService> is not installed.
trans-unit.target: En `InvalidOperationException` oppstår hvis det <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService>er ikke installert.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService>

trans-unit.source: If there is no state history for a newly created instance, state history is created without the instance being started.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det er ingen logg for nyopprettede forekomsten, opprettes Logg uten forekomsten startes.

trans-unit.source: Gets the latest definition of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowActivity"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter den seneste definisjonen av den <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowActivity"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: This property only returns a copy of the workflow definition and never the live instance tree.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen bare returnerer en kopi av arbeidsflytdefinisjonen og aldri treet live forekomst.

trans-unit.source: Therefore, the activity tree that is returned by this property cannot be used to query for run-time values.
trans-unit.target: Derfor aktivitetstreet som returneres av denne egenskapen kan ikke brukes i spørringen, til kjøretid verdier.

trans-unit.source: The latest definition of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowActivity"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Siste definisjonen av den <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowActivity"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: If the workflow has already completed, the current <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowActivity"></xref> cannot be retrieved, so the previous definition is retrieved.
trans-unit.target: Hvis arbeidsflyten er allerede fullført, gjeldende <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowActivity"> </xref> ikke kan hentes, slik at den forrige definisjonen hentes.
